bu nafaqat kinoya bo'ldi,

00:02:31.849 --> 00:02:34.144
balki sarkazm ham.

00:02:34.144 --> 00:02:35.354
Ammo, bitta "lekini" bor.

00:02:35.354 --> 00:02:38.525
Sarkazm doimo og'zaki kinoya birga 
kelishiga qaramay,

00:02:38.525 --> 00:02:42.069
og'zaki kinoya doim ham sarkastik 
bo'lavermaydi.

00:02:42.069 --> 00:02:44.363
Og'zaki kinoya shundayki, unda 
aytilgan gap

00:02:44.363 --> 00:02:46.844
nazarda tutilayotgan gapning aksi 
bo'lsa bo'ldi.

00:02:46.844 --> 00:02:50.284
Sarkazmda esa biroz zaharhandalik bo'ladi.

00:02:50.284 --> 00:02:51.263
Lekin ba'zida,

00:02:51.263 --> 00:02:53.847
shunday ham bo'ladiki, aytilgan gapda 
yana bitta

